Each card is made using a premium matte 325 GSM postcard. This card has a smooth matte finish that produces beautiful colour and perfect detail in the image. Each card has a blank white face on the reverse. Four black envelopes are included.

name: Indian Animals Temporary Tattoos by Deborah Ballinger
description:
Illustrated by Deborah Ballinger, these tattoos are printed with non-toxic ink and are are safe for children 5 years +

Instructions do come included, but for your reference please see below instructions:

1. Pick a smooth, clean and dry area
2. remove the transparent film and place face down on your skin
3. Wet the whole of the backing paper with a damp cloth and wait for 20 seconds
4. Carefully slide the backing paper away to reveal your new tattoo!

Care instructions:
1. Your new tattoo should last approximately 2-5 days depending in area of application.
2. Tattoos are waterproof
3. To remove early use baby oil or alcohol
4. Avoid contact with eyes
5. Do not apply to broken or sensitive skin


This tattoo pack comes with 4 different designs; two roller birds, 2 small butteflies, a benagl tiger and an elephant.

This Three Penny Lilac Estampe necklace, is approximately 2cm diameter, with silver plated 18 chain and setting (both lead and nickel free) with glass cabochon.

name: Twin Peaks Cufflinks by Kate Rowland
description:
Designed and handmade by Kate Rowland.

The design has been hand-drawn and engraved using a laser cutter.

Each cuff link is approximately 1.5cm x 1.5cm. They will be packaged in a recycled cotton padded gift box.

name: Owl Brooch by Young Explorer
description:
Designed and handmade by Young Explorer.

This owl brooch has been hand drawn onto white shrink plastic, with a silver coloured brooch back securely fastened onto the back.

Measures approximately 5cm tall.

name: Killer Whale Brooch by Young Explorer
description:
Designed and handmade by Young Explorer.

This Killer Whale brooch has been hand drawn onto shrink plastic with a silver coloured brooch back glued securely onto the back.

Measures approximately 4cm across.

name: Wooden Owl Brooch Nicola Jayne
description:
Designed and handmade by Nicola Jayne Designs, here in Nottingham.

This brooch has been laser cut with a denim style surface pattern. 

There is an antique bronze coloured brooch backing glued securely on the back.

Measures approximately 6cm tall.

name: Happy Raindrop Brooch by Debbie Greenaway
description:
This cute happy raindrop brooch has been designed and handmade by Debbie Greenaway.

Hand painted in blue onto laser cut wood, with a smiley face.

Measures approximately 3cm long, with a silver coloured brooch back.

name: Wooden Hedgehog Earrings by Ginger Pickle
description:
Designed and handmade by Ginger Pickle.

These Wooden Hedgehog Earrings are laser cut from 3mm birch plywood and are glued securely to silver plated nickel free earring studs.

The earrings are coated in Danish oil to protect the wood and give it a beautiful finish. They are very small and measure approx 1.2 x 0.9 cm

name: Wooden Elephant Earrings by Ginger Pickle
description:
These cute Wooden Elephant Earrings by Ginger Pickle have been laser cut from 3mm birch plywood. They are attached to silver plated nickel free stud backs and close with a butterfly clasp.

The earrings are coated in Danish oil to protect the wood and give it a beautiful finish. The earrings measure approx. 1.5cm x 1.2 cm.

name: Kitty Post Earrings by Andsmile
description:
Designed and handmade by AndSmile.

They are about 1.7cm tall and 1.5cm wide and made from shrink plastic and are hand drawn with permanent markers and varnished with gloss varnish for protection. Post earrings with a butterfly clutch backing.

***Please take care with those earrings! Occasional drizzle or a little bit of rain will be fine but please be nice to them and they will last long! Not suitable for small children.
